text.tspan: GDP per head vs share of services in employment, 1949 to 2010
The vertical axis shows historical estimates of the employment share in the service sector. The horizontal axis shows
GDP per head after adjusting for inflation (figures are in 2011 international US dollars) and uses multiple benchmarks
GDP per capita (2011 US$, multiple benchmarks)
Source: Our World In Data based on Herrendorf et al. (2014) and GGDC-10 (2015), Maddison Project Database (2018)
